```java
###################
# First build stage
###################

FROM maven:3.8.4-openjdk-11-slim as build

COPY .mvn .mvn
COPY mvnw .
COPY pom.xml .
COPY src src

RUN ./mvnw package

####################
# Second build stage
####################

FROM openjdk:11-jre-slim-buster

COPY --from=build target/my-project-1.0.jar .

EXPOSE 8080

ENTRYPOINT ["java", "-jar", "my-project-1.0.jar"]
```
